1. *Budimo* učtivi prema gostima. (Let's be polite towards the guests.)
2. Molim vas, *budite* tihi, deca spavaju. (Please be quiet, the children are sleeping.)
3. *Budimo* realni, nemamo dovoljno vremena. (Let's be realistic, we don't have enough time.)
4. Neka oni *budu* prvi koji će pomoći. (Let them be the first ones to help.)
5. Ako ne *budete* pažljivi, mogli biste se povrediti. (If you're not careful, you could get hurt.)
6. *Budimo* srećni što imamo jedni druge. (Let's be happy that we have each other.)
7. Rekao sam ti da *budem* ovde u pet sati. (I told you I'll be here at five o'clock.)
8. Nadam se da će sutra *biti* lep dan. (I hope tomorrow will be a nice day.)
9. *Budite* pažljivi kada vozite automobil. (Be careful when driving a car.)
10. Uvek *sam* hteo da *budem* pisac. (I've always wanted to be a writer.)